Welcome to our mirror server!

Here you can find copies of data found elsewhere. It is mirrored simply for our convenience (i.e. distributing software updates). All content is used according to its copyright (please let us know if we missed something, so that we can take any content down that shouldn't be available for download). Nevertheless you may download anything you find in this directory. Please don't index this site. It is not meant to be found in search engines. If you download software archives such as tar files or ISO images, please make sure that you check the appropriate checksums and cryptographic signatures!

Please note that the server configuration has been changed to SSL/TLS-only! This means that you can continue to use old URLs to this site, but you have to change http:// to https://.

Please note that the server configuration has been changed to limit access to browsers and clients equipped with a X.509 certificate from our own Certificate Authority! We have decided to do this because we wish to avoid accidental data leaks and wish to control access to this web server.
